title: Sweet Potato Fries
directions: Stir together olive oil, thyme, salt, and garlic powder in a medium bowl. Add sweet potato, and toss well to coat.

Lightly coat air fryer basket with cooking spray. Place sweet potatoes in single layer in the basket, and cook in batches at 400Â°F until tender on the inside and lightly browned on the outside, 14 minutes, turning fries over halfway through cooking.
ingredients: 2 (6-oz.) sweet potatoes, peeled and cut into 1/4-inch sticks
